high_descs: Walk around the low table from the left side to approach the middle of the sofa.
Pick up an apple from the plate on the sofa.
Take a tiny step to the left.
Put the apple on a pan on the sofa.
Walk left along the side of the low table and approach the right side of the sofa.
Pick up the knife from the sofa.
Return to the middle of the sofa with apple there.
Slice the apple with the knife.
Stick the knife in the pan.
Pick up the pan.
Walk around the countertop and head to the kitchen counter with a microwave across the hall.
Place the pan next to the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple on a pan, cut it with a knife and take it to the kitchen countertop next to a microwave.

high_descs: Walk over to the sofa and stand in front of it.
Pick up the golden apple that is on the plate on the sofa.
Hold the pan in your hand and look around.
Put the apple back on the pan.
Walk around the sofa to get to the other side of the coffee table.
Pick up the knife that is on the sofa.
walk around the coffee table to get to the other side again.
Cut the apple that is on the sofa.
Pick up the plate with the cut apple and the knife/pan.
Turn around with the pan and start to walk.
Walk to the countertop with the plate.
Put the pan down next to the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Get an apple and cut it, take it to the countertop.

Pick up the apple from the plate on the couch.
Turn left to face the pan on the couch.
Put the apple on the pan on the couch.
Turn around and walk to the right side of the sofa.
Pick up the yellow knife from the couch.
Turn around and walk to the left of the couch,
Cut the apple on the plate with the knife.
Put the knife on the pan with the fruit.
Pick up the pan from the couch.
Walk around the countertop and turn left to walk to the counter next to the microwave.
Put the pan on the countertop.
